high_descs: Move forward toward the range and face the counter between the range and the coffee maker to the right.
Pick up the loaf of bread between the range to the left and the coffee maker to the right.
Turn left, move toward the window, turn right and face the range, and then look upwards at the microwave above the range.
Open the microwave, place the loaf of bread on the plate, microwave the loaf of bread, open the microwave, pick up the loaf bread, and then close the microwave.
Turn right and move toward the toaster, then turn left and face the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the loaf of bread in front of the coffee maker and to the right of the wine bottle on the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed loaf of bread on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Move forward to the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the left of the coffee maker.
Move to the microwave on your left
Open the microwave, heat the bread in the microwave for a few seconds and take the bread out of the microwave.
Move back to the counter with the coffee maker on your right.
Put the bread on the counter in front of and slightly left of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed loaf of bread on the counter by the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the bread to the right of the coffee maker.
Turn around and go to the microwave, above the stove.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Turn right, then turn left to face the counter with the coffee maker.
Place the bread on the counter, in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put warm bread on the counter.
